name: Circles of AI Life V1
description:
Randomized P5 simulation. Circles eat Squares, Triangles eat Circles. As agents eat they slowly absorb colour from their food. 

Controls: s: Show/Change settings, r: Reset Simulation, c: Cycle Colour Palette. Mouse Click: Add a Circle agent. The simulation randomizes on each load, to set specific settings open the settings menu (s), pause the simulation, change the values and press the refresh icon.
